  <brief_title>Self Medication With Oral Morphine After Total Knee Arthroplasty.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Self Medication With Oral Morphine After Total Knee Arthroplasty. A Randomised Controlled Trial Comparing Self Medication With Standard Nurse Dispensing. Is There a Difference in Morphine Consumption, Pain, Patient Satisfaction or Safety?</official_title>
